<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        background-color: #f0f4f8;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        border-radius: 16px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #3498db;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 300;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 40px;
      }
      .content h1 {
        margin-top: 0;
        color: #2c3e50;
        font-weight: 300;
      }
      .content p {
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #34495e;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        background-color: #3498db;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 16px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 30px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      }
      .button:hover {
        background-color: #2980b9;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #ecf0f1;
        color: #7f8c8d;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h2>Payroll Portal</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
        <p>We received a request to reset your password for the Payroll Portal. If you didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        <p>To reset your password, click the button below:</p>
        <a href="{{url}}" class="button">Reset Password</a>
        <p>If you're unable to click the button, copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
        <p>{{url}}</p>
        <p>This link will expire in 24 hours for security reasons.</p>
        <p>If you need further assistance, please contact our support team.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br />The Payroll Portal Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Payroll Portal. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>